TITLE: Configuring Unleash Client with Impression Event Handling in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: Complete example showing how to initialize Unleash client, start it, check for feature flags, and handle impression events with event listeners.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unleash/unleash/blob/main/website/docs/reference/impression-data.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const unleash = new UnleashClient({
  url: 'https://eu.unleash-hosted.com/hosted/proxy',
  clientKey: 'your-proxy-key',
  appName: 'my-webapp',
});

unleash.start();

unleash.on('ready', () => {
  unleash.isEnabled('my-feature-flag');
});

