DESCRIPTION: Svelte component for the main application logic, including habit display and date formatting.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unleash/unleash/blob/main/website/docs/feature-flag-tutorials/sveltekit/implementing-feature-flags-sveltekit.md#2025-04-21_snippet_2

