TITLE: Archiving Feature Flag
DESCRIPTION: HTTP DELETE request to archive a feature flag. Uses the HTTPX library to make the API call.
SOURCE: https://github.com/unleash/unleash/blob/main/website/docs/feature-flag-tutorials/rails/rails-examples.md#2025-04-21_snippet_7

LANGUAGE: ruby
CODE:
```
require 'httpx'

url = "<your-unleash-url>/api/admin/projects/:projectId/features/:featureName"
payload = {}
headers = {
  'Authorization': '<API_KEY_VALUE>'
}

response = HTTPX.delete(url, headers: headers)
puts response.body
```

